d examinations will be conducted.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiatvnews.com/news/india/breaking-coronavirus-gujarat-shuts-schools-colleges-covid19-598370|title=Coronavirus: Gujarat shuts all schools, colleges, cinema halls from tomorrow|last=Hardaha|first=Rashi|date=15 March 2020|website=www.indiatvnews.com|language=en|access-date=15 March 2020}}</ref> [[Bihar Public Service Commission]] (BPSC) has postponed all the recruitment exams till 31 March.<ref>{{cite web |title=BPSC assistant engineer main exam 2019 postponed amid coronavirus outbreak| url=https://m.hindustantimes.com/education/bpsc-assistant-engineer-main-exam-2019-postponed-amid-coronavirus-outbreak/story-rQzUCoRWC4NHWa7Gq0SQTN.html|website=Hindustan times|author=| date=14 March 2020}}</ref> [[Vaishno Devi]] Shrine Board issued an advisory asking non-resident Indians and foreigners not to visit the temple for 28 days after landing in India.<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/coronavirus-cases-in-india-live-news-latest-updates-march15/liveblog/74633220.cms|title=Coronavirus News Live Updates: Third case reported in Telangana|date=15 March 2020|work=Economic Times|access-date=15 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> The [[Tamil Nadu]] and [[Telangana]] governments declared closure of schools, malls and theatres till 31 March.<ref>{{Cite news|last=Narasimhan|first=T. E.|url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/current-affairs/coronavirus-tamil-nadu-closes-schools-malls-and-theatres-till-march-31-120031500446_1.html|title=Coronavirus: Tamil Nadu closes schools, malls and theatres till March 31|date=15 March 2020|work=Business Standard India|access-date=15 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.livemint.com/news/india/coronavirus-schools-colleges-malls-movie-theatres-to-be-closed-in-telangana-until-31-march-11584186142495.html|title=Coronavirus: Schools, movie theatres to be closed in Telangana until 31 March|date=14 March 2020|websi